request.description:
Sends a notification to specified channels. Bypasses Kafka and dispatches synchronously.

Required fields: eventId, eventType, userId, channels (non-empty), templateId.

Response (200):
```json
{
  "eventId": "evt-001-20250101",
  "success": true,
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Notification sent to 2 channels",
  "channelResults": {
    "email": {
      "success": true,
      "messageId": "msg-abc-123",
      "errorMessage": null
    },
    "sms": {
      "success": false,
      "messageId": null,
      "errorMessage": "Provider unavailable"
    }
  }
}
```
